description:
The course starts from teaching you the basics of solving equations and moves on to cover ares such as Quadratic Equations, Simultaneous Equations, Inequalities, Ranges, Variance, Travel and Work.

We start by learning how to solve each section correctly, and then work on how to answer them quickly, where I will show you some techniques which will help you save a lot of time at the test, and spend that extra time on other areas so that you can further improve your score.

Our goal is to get a perfect score at the test in the sections covered. Once you go through this course you will see how easy algebra really is, and you will fall in love with Math.
title: SAT Math Algebra - A step by step guide to a A+ in Algebra
